setAutoFlush(boolean) - Method in interface org.apache.hadoop.hbase.client.HTableInterface
Deprecated. in 0.96. When called with setAutoFlush(false), this function also set clearBufferOnFail to true, which is unexpected but kept for historical reasons. Replace it with setAutoFlush(false, false) if this is exactly what you want, or by HTableInterface.setAutoFlushTo(boolean) for all other cases.
